Analysis of the Target Image  
────────────────────────────
The scene shows two separate “tower‐like” assemblies of red, green, blue, and yellow blocks.  From bottom to top:

■ Smaller (Left) Tower  
• Bottom layer: a red “ring”‐shaped block.  
• Middle layer: two blocks side by side at the same height—a green rectangular block spanning horizontally and a blue cube.  
• Top layer: another matching red “ring” block.  

In total, the left tower has 3 vertical layers but 4 blocks (the middle layer contains two separate blocks).

■ Larger (Right) Tower  
• Bottom layer: a red “ring” block.  
• Above that: a horizontal green rectangular block.  
• Middle layer: two cubes (blue and yellow) side by side.  
• Next: another horizontal green rectangular block.  
• Top layer: a second red “ring” block.  

Hence the right tower has 5 vertical layers but 6 total blocks.

Matching to the Dictionary  
──────────────────────────
1. The red “ring” blocks match catalog index “6” (the tall red piece whose half‐cylindrical hole is oriented front‐to‐back as seen in the dictionary image).  
2. The green horizontal rectangular blocks match index “12.”  
3. The blue cube is index “7.”  
4. The yellow cube is index “11.”

Block List and Quantities  
─────────────────────────
• Red ring (#6): 4 copies total (2 per tower).  
• Green rectangular (#12): 3 copies total (1 in the left tower; 2 in the right).  
• Blue cube (#7): 2 copies total (1 per tower).  
• Yellow cube (#11): 1 copy (in the right tower only).

Assembly Instructions  
─────────────────────
{
  Step1: Move block with index 6      // Left tower bottom
  Step2: Move block with index 12     // Left tower green middle
  Step3: Move block with index 7      // Left tower blue middle
  Step4: Move block with index 6      // Left tower top

  Step5: Move block with index 6      // Right tower bottom
  Step6: Move block with index 12     // Right tower lower green
  Step7: Move block with index 7      // Right tower blue in center
  Step8: Move block with index 11     // Right tower yellow in center
  Step9: Move block with index 12     // Right tower upper green
  Step10: Move block with index 6     // Right tower top
}
